title: BEST Premier League Goals of the Decade | 2010 - 2019 | Part 1
description: This video features Wayne Rooney’s bicycle kick v Manchester City, Papiss Cissé’s wonder strike against Chelsea, Olivier Giroud’s scorpion kick against Crystal Palace and loads more!

title: BEST Premier League Goals of the Decade | 2010 - 2019 | Part 2
description: A compilation of the best goals scored in the Premier League throughout the last decade, 2010 - 2019. This video features Son Heung-min’s solo goal against Burnley, Dimitri Payet’s free-kick against Crystal Palace, Robin van Persie’s volley v Aston Villa, Kevin De Bruyne’s wonder strike against Newcastle United and loads more!

title: 100 INSANE Premier League skills but they get more impressive 🔥
